  intermissionLines:
  - speaker: Head Witch
    text: Two unrelated accidents in one evening is bad luck. Three would be a pattern.
  - speaker: Apprentice
    text: The burn marks on Orren's sleeve match the glass sigils from Mira's bag.
  - speaker: Head Witch
    text: Then someone cracked a ward-stone and let the spellwork splinter through the
      tavern. Prep the deeper table.
